[size=5][b]Why did you make it?[/b][/size]
[size=3]I made this because I prefer to manage mods manually rather than using a manager due to my potato pc, and did not want to have to edit files each time I wanted to play vanilla.

I also like learning new code-ish stuff, and figuring this out was fun :)[/size]

